Sentencas: Co-doped CeO2 (Ba0.10Ga0.10Ce0.80O3-delta) was synthesized via a cost-effective co-precipitation technique, and the electrochemical properties of the solid oxide fuel cell were studied.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of co-doped ceria-based electrolyte material for low temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The microstructural and surface morphological properties were investigated by XRD and SEM, respectively.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of co-doped ceria-based electrolyte material for low temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The structure of the prepared material was found to be cubic fluorite with an average crystallite size of 36 nm.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of co-doped ceria-based electrolyte material for low temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The ionic conductivity of the prepared BGC (Ba0.10Ga0.10Ce0.80O3-delta) electrolyte material was measured as 0.071 S cm(-1).
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of co-doped ceria-based electrolyte material for low temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The activation energy was found to be 0.46 eV using an Arrhenius plot.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of co-doped ceria-based electrolyte material for low temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The maximum power density and current density achieved were 375 mW cm(-2) and 893 mA cm(-2), respectively, at 650 degrees C with hydrogen as a fuel.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of co-doped ceria-based electrolyte material for low temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: This study shows that the prepared co-doped electrolyte material could be used as a potential electrolyte to lower the operating temperature of solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of co-doped ceria-based electrolyte material for low temperature solid oxide fuel cell
